body
    .section.hero.is-dark
      .container
        .content
          h1.title Job Market in Melbourne
          h2.title The story of job market in Melbourne
    
    .section
      .container
        .content
          h2 1. Melbourne Job Map
          p First, we will look at the number of employments and business establishments in Melbourne.
          p It is not surprising to see that <b>Melbourne CBD</b> is the most crowded area for work. The second and third places are Docklands and Southbank, Respectively.
          
          .columns
            .column.is-5
              #choro
            .column.is-7
              #step1stack

          p Next, we will explore which industry is the most popular in Melbourne.
            
    .section
      .container
        .content
          h2 2. Employment in each industry
          #step2tree

    .section
      .container
        .content
          h2 3. Number of jobs available VS Graduated students
          #step3bar
    
    .section
      .container
        .content
          h2 4. The biggest companies you can rely on:
          .columns
            .column.is-5
              p The top companies that are biggest in Melbourne are:
              ol.topcomp-list
                li 7-Eleven
                li RMIT
                li KFC
                li Parking
                li McDonald
            .column.is-7
              #step4line

    .section.hero.is-light
      .container
        .content
          h2 Acknowledgements
          h3 Data Sources
          ul.acknow
